{
  "name": "Power Word Heal",
  "_id": "matSplPowerWordH",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A wave of healing energy washes over one creature you can see within range. The target regains all its Hit Points. If the creature has any of the &amp;Reference[Blinded apply=false], &amp;Reference[Charmed apply=false], &amp;Reference[Dazed apply=false], &amp;Reference[Deafened apply=false], &amp;Reference[Frightened apply=false], &amp;Reference[Incapacitated apply=false], &amp;Reference[Paralyzed apply=false], &amp;Reference[Petrified apply=false], &amp;Reference[Poisoned apply=false], &amp;Reference[Possessed apply=false], &amp;Reference[Stunned apply=false], &amp;Reference[Unconscious apply=false], or &amp;Reference[Weakened apply=false] conditions, the conditions end. All levels of &amp;Reference[exhaustion apply=false] are removed, and all expended hit dice are restored. If the creature has the &amp;Reference[Prone apply=false] condition, it can use its Reaction to stand up.</p><section class=\"secret\" id=\"secret-TZTRxIEOucKFdjFi\"><p>Foundry Note</p><p>The <strong>Heal Fully</strong> activity is configured to heal 1,000 Hit Points such that any single creature can be healed fully.</p></section>",
